        <updateDate>2020-06-24T13:38:35Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Bad Lawmakers Accountability and Key Emends Act or the BLAKE Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a former Member of Congress from serving as a lobbyist until such former Member reimburses the Treasury for the amount paid as a settlement or award to an employee for a claim alleging harassment based on race, color, religion, sex, national origin, age, disability, or veteran status, or retaliation for reporting these types of harassment.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
